  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-800">Sugarcane Cultivation</h1>

  <div class="mb-12 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Sugarcane cultivation is an important agricultural practice worldwide, with a long history dating back centuries. It is valued for its versatility, providing not only sugar but also molasses, rum, ethanol, and other by-products. The cultivation of sugarcane plays a significant role in the economy of many countries, providing employment opportunities and contributing to food security.
    </p>
